    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/style.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/footer.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/about.css")

  body
    nav
      .logo
        i.fa-solid.fa-shield-cat.fa-flip
        | SoundScape

      .nav-links
        a(href='/') Home
        a(href='shows') Shows
        a(href='hosts') Hosts
        a(href='about') About Us
        a(href='login') Login

    header
      h1 Explore life's tapestry with SoundScape Podcast, where each episode is a journey, exploring life's wonders and mysteries through immersive sound design and compelling narratives

    main
      .about-container
        .our-mission
          h1 Our Mission
          p Our mission is to connect hearts and minds through the power of storytelling, bringing diverse voices and experiences to the forefront. We aim to inspire, educate, and entertain, fostering a global community united by a shared love for captivating narratives and profound insights.
        .Our-value
          h1 Our Values
          p Our core value lies in embracing authenticity, diversity, and creativity. We believe in the transformative power of storytelling to bridge gaps, spark curiosity, and cultivate a deeper understanding and appreciation of the world around us. Through our commitment to these principles, we strive to enrich the lives of our listeners and contribute positively to the global narrative.
        .founder
          h1 Founder
          p From our founder: 'At the heart of our podcast lies a passion for storytelling and a belief in its power to connect us all. We started this journey with a vision to create a space where diverse voices and stories could thrive, transcending boundaries and touching lives. Thank you for joining us on this incredible journey, and here's to the many adventures that lie ahead.'

    footer
      section
        .footer-logo
          i.fa-solid.fa-shield-cat
          | SoundScape
        p Stay tuned, stay inspired, and keep the conversations going with SoundScape. Connect, share, and dive deeper into the world of podcasts with us.

      section
        h2.footer-section-subheading Quick Links
        .footer-links
          a(href="index.html") Home
          a(href="shows.html") Shows
          a(href="hosts.html") Hosts
          a(href="about.html") About Us
          a(href="contact.html") Contact
          a(href="login.html") Login

      section
        h2.footer-section-subheading Contact Us
